4: <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Tennessee_(BB-43)" class="extiw" title="w:USS Tennessee (BB-43)">USS <i>Tennessee</i></a><br />
5: <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_West_Virginia_(BB-48)" class="extiw" title="w:USS West Virginia (BB-48)">USS <i>West Virginia</i></a><br />
