8: <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Pennsylvania_(BB-38)" class="extiw" title="w:USS Pennsylvania (BB-38)">USS <i>Pennsylvania</i></a><br />
9: <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ford_Island" class="extiw" title="w:Ford Island">Ford Island NAS</a><br />
