<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFWillmott1983">Willmott, H.P. (1983), <i>The Barrier and the Javelin: Japanese and Allied Pacific Strategies, February to June 1942</i>, Annapolis, MD: Naval Institute Press, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0870210920" class="internal">ISBN 0870210920</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Barrier+and+the+Javelin%3A+Japanese+and+Allied+Pacific+Strategies%2C+February+to+June+1942&amp;rft.aulast=Willmott&amp;rft.aufirst=H.P.&amp;rft.au=Willmott%2C+H.P.&amp;rft.date=1983&amp;rft.place=Annapolis%2C+MD&amp;rft.pub=Naval+Institute+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0870210920&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Attack_on_Pearl_Harbor"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
