<p><a name="Historic_documents" id="Historic_documents"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Attack_on_Pearl_Harbor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=30" title="Edit section: Historic documents">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Historic documents</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://ww2db.com/doc.php?q=45" class="external text" title="http://ww2db.com/doc.php?q=45" rel="nofollow">WW2DB: US Navy Report of Japanese Raid on Pearl Harbor</a></li>
